---
title: Rigatoni and Mini Turkey Meatballs with Sweet Peppers
description: It's pasta night and this dish is the perfect start to a fun family evening. The highlight are the mini meatballs, which are made for small hands and bellies. Rigatoni and peppers join the party in a rich Italian-spiced red sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rigatonis-et-mini-boulettes-de-dinde-84f39710.jpg
